metadata.name: Founding Membership Pass #2
metadata.description: ChainSpirit is a web 3.0 native liquor brand blurring digital and physical barriers. FOUNDING MEMBERSHIP PASS is your key to unleashing all the benefits and members-only experience of the ChainSpirit ecosystem. All members co-govern our Web 3.0 native alcoholic-beverages brand. Bring life to the IP of your Digital Collectibles(NFT) through our products by joining us.
